{"id":"summaries/2021-10-28-you-can-try-it-might-work-it-might-not-thats-just-luck","title":"You can try, it might work it might not, that's just luck","type":"summaries","html":"<p>Title-only one-line outcome-detachment aphorism from October 2021 by <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">Yahir</a> — <em>\"You can try, it might work it might not, that's just luck.\"</em> Sibling phrasing to <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disconnected-from-outcome\">disconnected from outcome</a>. Same-day companion to <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2021-10-28-beilieve-in-your-self-no-matter-what\">2021 10 28 beilieve in your self no matter what</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/yahir-gonzalez\">yahir gonzalez</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disconnected-from-outcome\">disconnected from outcome</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/fear-of-not-doing\">fear of not doing</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/manifesto-style-note\">manifesto style note</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"summaries/2021-10-28-beilieve-in-your-self-no-matter-what","label":"Believe in your self no matter what"},{"id":"concepts/disconnected-from-outcome","label":"Disconnected From the Outcome"},{"id":"concepts/fear-of-not-doing","label":"Fear of Not Doing"},{"id":"concepts/manifesto-style-note","label":"Manifesto-style note"},{"id":"entities/yahir-gonzalez","label":"Yahir Gonzalez"}]}
